{"tid":633556,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ [IT]年初兩旅行社被黑客入侵及勒索 警拘一IT男","createTime":"2018-04-18T12:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T12:18:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb34fe851c291c05dc1469b090b10213d4ebd82","tid":633556,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"今年一月初，本港兩間旅行社疑遭黑客連環入侵，再被勒索比特幣贖回客戶資料。警方於1月3日先後接獲大航假期及金怡假期負責人報案，稱遭黑客入侵網上系統盜取大量客戶資料，並遭對方勒索1元比特幣（巿值約12.2萬港元）以贖回被盜資料，網絡安全及科技罪案調查科接手跟進，事隔3日在長洲拘捕30歲黑客。<br />\n<br />\n據悉警方當時逐一調查案發當日每名登入者，找出部份可疑IP位址，發現疑犯以迂迴方式透過外國伺服器隱藏身份非法入侵，警方最終鎖定疑人身份，於其長洲寓所將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180418/58089434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F58089434&d=ee90mIes5nct%2B2vf3A%2FOTmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=c2eded11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F58089434&h=40e61607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180418/58089434</a>"},{"pid":"6958d9a7b3618f788dbb7a4bc0ecf63382250bd8","tid":633556,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"IT是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d377b3a56a245a1e7e26e8b21179964ef123857f","tid":633556,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"IT=crime"},{"pid":"91eceb5238e9bf3edff70b9f562534d99e229fba","tid":633556,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"用proxy上咪捉唔到"}]}